  <brief_title>Bunionectomy Study for Postoperative Analgesia (EPOCH 1)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Randomized, Double Blind, Saline Placebo and Active Controlled, Multicenter Study of HTX 011 Via Local Administration for Postoperative Analgesia and Decreased Opioid Use Following Unilateral Simple Bunionectomy</official_title>
