  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a Phase 3, randomized, double-blind, saline placebo- and active-controlled,
      multicenter study to evaluate the analgesic efficacy and safety of HTX 011 administered via
      local administration into the surgical site in subjects undergoing bunionectomy.
    </textblock>
